short_description: This US-SJ 65/FM800 model equipment is used for production of polypropylene material bags. The equipment has a product production capacity of up to 55 kg per hour and a total power of 50 kW. The size of the equipment weighing 3500 kg is 4.5 * 2.8 * 4.5 m. The description also shows other models of this equipment, and their prices differ from each other.

Tavsifda ushbu uskunaning boshqa modellari ham aks etgan va ularning narxlari bir-biridan farqlanadi.
